snippet.title: Oriental Valley - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
🆕🆕Get ready to start a modern rural life in Oriental Valley!
Oriental Valley is a life sim and will be available on PC in Spring 2024.
Build a modern new home, learn modern agriculture, chat with friends, and enjoy your happy life here! And beautiful scenery is waiting for you to explore.

💓➡️Add it to your Wishlist: 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2201930/Oriental_Valley/
💬➡️Join our Discord for more information:
https://discord.gg/szu4y3QsbT
